OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the afternoon. Becoming
OL,7,Fcloudy overnight with low cloud and
OL,8,Ffog coming off the North Sea and
OL,9,Fspreading slowly westwards by the
OL,10,Fmorning. A mild night for most, cooler
OL,11,Falong the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FLow cloud and fog
OL,14,Fdissipating inland resulting in warm
OL,15,Fafternoon sunshine. Cloud lingers
OL,16,Falong the coast with a moderate
OL,17,Feasterly breeze resulting in a cooler
OL,18,Ffeel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
