OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart for some on Sunday, sunny
OL,7,Fafternoon for most. Largely sunny
OL,8,Fconditions on Monday with coastal
OL,9,Fcloud. Patchy cloud Tuesday morning,
OL,10,Fbrightening up later. Temperatures
OL,11,Fslightly above average inland.
